response.overview: May 24th, 2009 :: The Colony and F.I.S.T. rivalry boils over in a landmark lucha de apuesta, where Fire Ant and Soldier Ant wager both their masks against the hair of Icarus and Chuck Taylor! Glacier and D-Lo Brown combine forces. Why? WHY NOT! In trios action, Delirious joins UltraMantis Black and Crossbones to take on the Super Smash Brothers and Create-A-Wrestler! Matches featured:  1. Los Ice Creams vs The Roughnecks  2. Ophidian vs Arik Cannon  3. The Order of the Neo Solar Temple vs The Saturday Night Slam Masters  4. Vin Gerard & Colin Delaney vs D-Lo Brown & Glacier  5. 2.0 vs Sea Donsters  6. Incoherence, Cheech & Cloudy vs Jigsaw, Helios, Lince Dorado & Mike Quackenbush  7. Eddie Kingston vs Claudio Castagnoli  8. Lucha de Apuesta Match F.I.S.T. vs The Colony.
response.title: Chikara Aniversario Yang
